This paper proposes a new approach for active learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper focuses on designing a practical active learning method that considers both informativeness and representativeness. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
